Usage: setIsolatedCutRule [-help] [-cornerSpacing <float>] -spacing <float> [-layer <string> ]

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
-cornerSpacing <float>     # Specifies the maiximum distance spacing2 for the
                           # corner check (float, optional)
-layer <string>            # Sets the spacing rule for specified cut layers
                           # (string, optional)
-spacing <float>           # Specifies the maximum distance between the cut
                           # being validated to its nearest cut (float, required)